dataset.notes:
The data contained within the raw files is the automatic cycle counts for the City Centre Cordon sites and has the following results for each month from January to March 2019:

Hourly figures
Daytime Total: Total count from 6am to 8pm inclusive
Daily AM Peak
Daily PM Peak
24 Hour Daily Total

In addition each month has:
Monthly Daily Totals - Per Hour
Monthly Weekday Totals (Monday - Friday)
Total number of journeys per month

For ease of reference, there are 2 location plans showing all of the Counters with their respective Site ID's.
